  <h1>Foundational Principles for AI Coding</h1>
</div>
<div class="content">
  <div class="principle">
    <p class="principle-title">System Over Tool</p>
    <p class="principle-text">Focus on building robust, reusable systems (PIV Loop, custom commands) rather than relying on specific tools or models</p>
  </div>
  <div class="principle">
    <p class="principle-title">Avoid Over-engineering</p>
    <p class="principle-text">Prioritize simplicity and conciseness in planning to prevent errors and hallucinations</p>
  </div>
  <div class="principle">
    <p class="principle-title">Delegate Code, Own Validation</p>
    <p class="principle-text">Let AI handle implementation, but maintain full ownership of planning and validation phases</p>
  </div>
</div>
